    "description": "<strong>Midnight Arrow</strong> is an atmospheric puzzle platformer that uses a retro art style. <strong>Hop</strong> on platforms and <strong>jump</strong> on walls to <strong>explore</strong> a <strong>vast immersive platforming world</strong>. <strong>Discove</strong> the different types of arrows and use them to <strong>solve puzzles</strong> and <strong>illuminate</strong> the darkened world around you! Oh and did I mention you can now create your own levels? 👀<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/c14dce253f20ce336c8af6dd7d8372cf.poster.avif?t=1720082471\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/c14dce253f20ce336c8af6dd7d8372cf.webm?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/c14dce253f20ce336c8af6dd7d8372cf.mp4?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tight smooth platforming 🦘<br></li><li>Optional quests 🏆<br></li><li>Collectables 🍭<br></li><li>Skins 👕<br></li><li>6 areas with new mechanics 🏔️<br></li><li>New Puzzles in every area 🧩<br></li><li>Level Editor 🛠️<br></li><li>Speedrunning Stuff ⏰</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Light up your path</strong> </h2>through the dark caverns using fire arrows.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/553592f19c4ebb9192eec120a1d093eb.poster.avif?t=1720082471\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/553592f19c4ebb9192eec120a1d093eb.webm?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/553592f19c4ebb9192eec120a1d093eb.mp4?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve puzzles</strong> </h2>than test your aim, platforming, and dexterity abilities, all at the same time. You need to do both puzzle-solving and platforming at the same time and if you are extra good at platforming you can even cheese the game for some speedrunning advantage! 🧀<br>Each area brings new mechanics that add to the complexity of the platforming and the challenges of the puzzles. The game has a total of 6 areas each with its unique mood and playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/42226ae7a21b6198e9d753d1b4b24bdb.poster.avif?t=1720082471\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/42226ae7a21b6198e9d753d1b4b24bdb.webm?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/42226ae7a21b6198e9d753d1b4b24bdb.mp4?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use different arrows</strong> </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/bbe02af5d7b237bfb5f0660cf3c67ddf.poster.avif?t=1720082471\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/bbe02af5d7b237bfb5f0660cf3c67ddf.webm?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/bbe02af5d7b237bfb5f0660cf3c67ddf.mp4?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve optional quests!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/b35f40c4e7c96a3108c27cfabd7d8fa5.poster.avif?t=1720082471\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/b35f40c4e7c96a3108c27cfabd7d8fa5.webm?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/b35f40c4e7c96a3108c27cfabd7d8fa5.mp4?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>And Make your own levels!🤩</strong></h2>The game comes with the level editor integrated! You have all the features accessible (except NPCs) so you can create your own levels as cool as the original ones! Check this tutorial out!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/e344db6ac8778aff1d83c8d402f92083.poster.avif?t=1720082471\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/e344db6ac8778aff1d83c8d402f92083.webm?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/e344db6ac8778aff1d83c8d402f92083.mp4?t=1720082471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br>",
